    <h2>About Ignacio Farm</h2>
    <p>
      Ignacio Farm is a private rest villa in Lumban, Laguna—crafted as a modern sanctuary for family leisure, quiet retreats, and intimate gatherings surrounded by nature and serenity.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Design Philosophy</h2>
    <p>
      To design a modern private villa for our client, a close-knit family seeking a peaceful and exclusive retreat in Lumban, Laguna. The project should reflect contemporary comfort while embracing natural surroundings—emphasizing privacy, serenity, and a warm atmosphere ideal for restful stays, family bonding, and intimate celebrations within a thoughtfully designed, nature-integrated space.
    </p>
